skdetail:

des:
Finding true love is never easy. Knowing if your man is really interested in you is always a challenge. Take the "Does He Love Me", test and uncover whether your man is a keeper or should be kicked to the curb.

<Alexa, open does he love me> to start the alexa skill.
<start test> To begin the love study
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
